name: United 737-824 Onboard Takeoff and Landing (DEN-SAN) ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everyone, here's a new travel video, featuring the second leg of my trip to San Diego, from Denver. You can't see much anyway, so I figured I would upload both flights as one video. Sorry for the lousy focus on landing. You can see my favorite spotting location at 2:32, the Aladdin Parking Garage :) Hope you enjoy!
